title: Number of divorces in Sweden 2008 to 2018
summary: Overall Number of divorces has increased over the Year.

Number of divorces is slightly increasing from 2009 to 2010, roughly constant from 2010 to 2012, slightly increasing from 2012 to 2013, slightly decreasing from 2013 to 2015, and finally roughly constant from 2015 to 2017.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2012 and 2013.
Maximum Number of divorces, about 26933.0 was reported at Year 2013
Minimum Number of divorces about 23534.0 was reached at Year 2009
